author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
🎟️ To come and see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK from January 2026, find tickets here:

Having been recently schooled by BBC Breakfast presenters in the art of interviewing, I took those lessons into my own interview with Sleaford Mods' frontman Jason Williamson. Bizarrely, there was no mention of my mobile phone usage and I got his name right so it turned out quite well! 

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The latest Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory
